Recorded By: DECHO Pgs: 1

CLARK COUNTY RECORDER
Src: FRONT COUNTER
Ofc: MAIN OFFICE
WHEREAS, pursuant to the provisions of NRS 360.473, of Nevada revised statutes, a certificate of
delinquency was filed in the office of the County Recorder of Nye County, Nevada on 02/04/2021 as
document number 947992 of official records, and
WHEREAS said filing gave rise to a lien upon all the real property in said county owned or afterwards
acquired by NAGEL STEPHANIE D dba:
NOW, for good cause and pursuant to the provisions of NRS 360.475, of Nevada Revised statutes, the
Department of Taxation hereby wholly releases and discharges from said lien all of the real property in
Nye County, Nevada owned by, NAGEL STEPHANIE D dba: ---
Dated this 16th day of February. 2021, in Carson City, Nevada, Phone Number (775) 684-2000.
DEPARTMENT OF TAXATION
